This paper discusses the privacy and anonymity of users in P2P networks, which is a topic related to computer security (cs.CR) and computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also analyzes the usage of Tor, which is a tool for anonymous communication (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the risks of privacy violation, which is a topic related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and software engineering (cs.SE).
